  <chapter|Chunk Parameters>

  <\nf-chunk|test:chunk-params:sub>
    I see a ${THING},

    a ${THING} of colour ${colour},\ 

    and looking closer =\<less\>\\chunkref{test:chunk-params:sub:sub}(${colour})\<gtr\>
  </nf-chunk||<tuple|THING|colour>>

